      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pierson%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Ferns from Pierson are shipped across the globe, where they adorn floral arrangements and decorative displays worldwide.",
